data.description: Beautiful one story home, nestled on nearly quarter of an acre in desirable neighborhood.  This home features LVP Flooring, Open Floor Plan, Tall Ceilings, an abundance of Natural Light, and a 2 Car Garage.  The Gourmet Chef Kitchen offers White Cabinets, Stainless Steel Appliances, a Range Hood, a Pantry, and a huge Kitchen Island with Quartz Counters.  The kitchen opens up to a large Family Room with high ceilings and a Dining Space.  There is also a separate Dining Room with trey ceiling.  The oversized Master Suite has a large Walk In Closet.  The en-suite bath offers dual sinks, Tile Floors, White Cabinets, and a Stand Up Shower.  The Guest Bedrooms are spacious with ample storage.  Step out back to the Patio and enjoy the privacy of the backyard.  Welcome Home!
